text: Electra, My Love () is a 1974 Hungarian drama movie directed by Miklós Jancsó and starring Mari Törőcsik, György Cserhalmi, József Madaras, Mária Bajcsay, Lajos Balázsovits, Gabi Jobba. ==Other websites== * Category:1974 drama movies Category:Hungarian movies Category:Movies directed by Miklós Jancsó
title: Electra, My Love
